//
// Target: AArch64 (ARM64) — ARMv8-A and later
// ABI: AAPCS64 (ARM Architecture Procedure Call Standard for 64-bit)
// 
// Supported targets:
//   - aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu   (Linux userspace)
//   - aarch64-apple-darwin        (macOS Apple Silicon)
//   - aarch64-unknown-none        (Bare metal / Quanta OS kernel)
//
